    RegistryGrpc
    public static final class RegistryGrpc.RegistryBlockingStub
extends io.grpc.stub.AbstractBlockingStub<RegistryGrpc.RegistryBlockingStub>
    A stub to allow clients to do synchronous rpc calls to service Registry. 
     The Registry service allows teams to manage descriptions of APIs.
